1. *Terenu* je pokriven smećem. (The ground was covered with garbage.) 
2. On je završio trening na *terenu* u parku. (He finished his training at the field in the park.) 
3. Fudbaleri su se spremali za utakmicu na *terenu*. (The soccer players were getting ready for the match on the field.) 
4. Neki ljudi često šetaju *terenom*. (Some people often walk the field.) 
5. Osnovna škola ima veliki *teren*. (The elementary school has a large field.) 
6. On je istrčao preko *terena*. (He ran across the field.) 
7. Dete je igralo loptu na *terenu*. (The child was playing ball on the field.)